Query Strings is: additional data added to the end of a http request in the form of name value pairs

example: 

mysite.com/blog/news?page=2

Starts with the ? so its the second page of news in the blog

The start of the query string always starts with a ? 

Name vale pair: person=ryu

Add another name value pair: & 

Name value pair: dept=marketing

example: mysite.com/contact?person=ryu7dept=marketing


